@{c}@{h3}COMMANDS
@{c}@{h4}in multiple choice games

The multiple choice games are played by repeatedly selecting one of up to three
given choices by pressing key @{i}1@{ui}, @{i}2@{ui} or @{i}3@{ui}. Pressing the @{i}4@{ui} key will open a command
mode where you can enter one of the following commands:

           @{b}save@{ub}: Save the current game position to file.
           @{b}load@{ub}: Load a previously saved game position from file.
        @{b}restart@{ub}: Restart the game.
@{b}pictures on@{ub}/@{b}off@{ub}: Turn pictures on or off.
           @{b}help@{ub}: Print general help or help for the given command.

