@{c}@{h3}COLOSSAL ADVENTURE

@{b}Colossal Adventure@{ub} is a complete, full-size version of the classic mainframe
game @{b}Adventure@{ub} with all the treasures, creatures, rooms and puzzles of the
original. And we have added 70 bonus locations to the end-game. No one else
gives you this. Visit Colossal Cavern and meet the giant snake, Chinese dragon
and mercenary Troll, and watch out for the knives of the evil dwarfs. No true
adventurer should miss this game.

             @{b}Year@{ub}: @{i}1986@{ui} (@{i}1982@{ui})
@{b}Original platform@{ub}: @{i}Atari ST@{ui}
     @{b}Game version@{ub}: @{i}V3@{ui}
    @{b}Graphics type@{ub}: @{i}Line-drawn@{ui}

