@{c}@{h3}ADVENTURE QUEST

Hundreds of years have passed since the time of @{b}Colossal Adventure@{ub} and evil
forces are invading the land. One hope remains: you must discover the Old Roads
to the Dark Tower, fortress of the Demon Lord. Only there can you defeat him.
The way is long and dangerous, through nine different regions of forest,
desert, mountain, water, fire etc., but with cunning you can make it to the
final confrontation with Agaliarept.

             @{b}Year@{ub}: @{i}1986@{ui} (@{i}1982@{ui})
@{b}Original platform@{ub}: @{i}Atari ST@{ui}
     @{b}Game version@{ub}: @{i}V3@{ui}
    @{b}Graphics type@{ub}: @{i}Line-drawn@{ui}

