@{c}@{h3}SNOWBALL

The massive starship, @{i}Snowball 9@{ui}, is carrying two million hibernating
colonists to Eden, fertile planet in the Eridani star system, in this top
selling game with over 7000 locations. The Snowball has been hijacked and
is heading into the sun in this first part of the @{b}Silicon Dreams@{ub} trilogy.
You'll meet Waldroids, Nightingales and other strange robots in this massive
science fiction adventure. But the most baffling puzzle, according to many
players, is how to use the control room computer.

             @{b}Year@{ub}: @{i}1986@{ui} (@{i}1983@{ui})
@{b}Original platform@{ub}: @{i}Atari ST@{ui}
     @{b}Game version@{ub}: @{i}V3@{ui}
    @{b}Graphics type@{ub}: @{i}Line-drawn@{ui}

