The House of the Red Moon is a weird place, haunted by arcane powers from the
mythical past. It is the only place where one might rise from Sorcerer's
Apprentice to powerful Wizard, yet cheat the Price of Magik. @{b}The Price of Magik@{ub}
is the sequel to @{b}Red Moon@{ub}.

             @{b}Year@{ub}: @{i}1988@{ui} (@{i}1986@{ui})
@{b}Original platform@{ub}: @{i}Amiga@{ui}
