@{c}@{h3}KNIGHT ORC

@{b}Knight Orc@{ub} is Level 9's most innovative and fun-packed adventure to date.
Set in three parts, it casts you as an oppressed orc in a magical world where
all is not as it first seems. For generations humans have been persecuting orcs,
and now it's time to get your own back. @{b}Knight Orc@{ub} is a challenging game
which is truly interactive. Each character leads its own life in the game, and
their actions can affect you and the outcome of the adventure. Communication
with other characters, learning spells and solving puzzles are all a vital part
of the game if you are to escape the mystical world and take revenge on
humankind.

             @{b}Year@{ub}: @{i}1987@{ui}
@{b}Original platform@{ub}: @{i}PC@{ui} (game files), @{i}Amiga@{ui} (picture files)
     @{b}Game version@{ub}: @{i}V4@{ui}
